{"tid":1550664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌！好心啦！你地唔好再諗自殺","createTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:00.000Z","uid":39277,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b418bc2616fa1cb29205eefa8f2c21a66b4f1e6c","tid":1550664,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:55.000Z","msg":"自殺係好撚戇鳩<br />\n即係等於你完場前自己射入自己龍<br />\n輸零比一完場<br />\n<br />\n人生不如意事本就十常八九<br />\n尋日同今日遇到啲事仆街<br />\n可能聽日有大獎等緊你地呢<br />\n<br />\n有千幾個手足被捕<br />\n幾條人命<br />\n三隻眼<br />\n有幾多手足係新屋嶺畀人虐待<br />\n難得我地仲有自由之軀<br />\n我地要為唔能夠行出嚟嘅人戰鬥落去<br />\n<br />\n如果你依一刻仲想死<br />\n你當你已經死咗<br />\n無人知道死咗之後嘅世界係點<br />\n以後每一日你都係賺咗返嚟<br />\n你可以選擇繼續戰鬥或者做你鍾意做嘅事"},{"pid":"63ca81637cdd37ad3785acfc7312cf90114c060b","tid":1550664,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:03:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4fcc2855c02dc787b2b689cfb2acbb812b12ece","tid":1550664,"uid":148332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"前題係佢地真係自殺"},{"pid":"26576ea6e94a1e99182f946aa08c3101a9c73e79","tid":1550664,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:05.000Z","msg":"要輸都拉埋對家一齊輸，唔好自己認輸！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>九月八，遮打見！</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZUq8PfJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUq8PfJ.png&h=6ed8457a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外以下口號可以一記：<br />\n-Free Hong Kong, Democracy now!<br />\n-Fight for Freedom, Stand with Hong Kong!<br />\n-Five Demands, Not one less!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">練定美國國歌一齊唱K</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=8becc05b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a>"},{"pid":"c9329e275b43eb1eb833cb8332efc44364c96916","tid":1550664,"uid":16871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:18:54.000Z","msg":"同意 塞翁失馬焉知非福一日未到結局你都唔知道 個結果係好定壞 但係只要你自殺就一定係最壞嘅結果"},{"pid":"1129af362d1396f294c6a37620dce8f6c425d512","tid":1550664,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"係跳就攬一隻狗一齊跳"}]}